We are looking for experienced Java Developers.

Join our new team in Oradea if you:
* are a passionate software engineer, who likes solving difficult problems, have great debugging skills and attention to detail. 
* feel that the technology stack you are working with gets old and opportunities to learn new things are too far.
* want to offer the best and learn from the best.

Required competencies:

Must: 
•	Java EE & SE
•	EJB
•	JPA 
•	JAX-WS
•	JAX-RS
•	JAXB
•	JSF
•	JTA, 
•	HTML/CSS/JavaScript
•	XML/XSLT/XSD
•	Ant

Nice to have:
•	Spring
•	IBM WebSphere
•	IBM MQ Server
•	IBM DB2
•	Hibernate

We value: 
•	Respect
•	Reliability
•	Striving for excellence 





			    $(document).ready(function() { 
			    var allVideos = $('.job-video-container object, .job-video-container embed, .job-video-container iframe'); 
			    var oldWidth = allVideos.width();
			    var oldHeight =  allVideos.height();
			    var aspectRatioOS = oldHeight/oldWidth; 
			    allVideos.removeAttr('height').removeAttr('width');
			    function resizeVideoOSJS(){
				allVideos.attr('style', 'max-width: 600px; width: 100%;');
				var widthInit = allVideos.width();
				var heightInit = widthInit * aspectRatioOS;
				allVideos.attr('style', 'max-width: 600px; width: 100%; min-height: 220px; height: '+ heightInit +'px;');
				//.attr('width',  widthInit).attr('height', allVideos.height())    
			    }
			    resizeVideoOSJS();
				    window.onresize = resizeVideoOSJS; 
			    });
